":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"跟電子香一樣<br />\n做個樣 呃神騙鬼"},{"pid":"28df81bb61f4b83ee996873b8cefade0989c5c29","tid":258593,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"wfc🤷🏻&zwj;♀️"},{"pid":"2c22e3564407f2fbdc647a668253800b4ab50139","tid":258593,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:48:58.000Z","msg":"點解李卓人好似多左兩撇鬚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03b9afce560323eba685371188c97a9fa4c602a","tid":258593,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"中化題目  網上祭祖<br />\n終於實現了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留個言當去左維園"},{"pid":"d4834b2e92dceae413dfde2cf964bb3efde5df87","tid":258593,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100610/large/10lp2p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100610%2Flarge%2F10lp2p10.jpg&h=b191e101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">食環署推出網上拜山</span></span><br />\n<br />\n懷念先人，唔使等到拜山先講嘢。骨灰龕位供不應求，食環署為平息民怨，近年力推骨灰紀念花園同海葬，今日仲推出網上拜山網頁，孝子賢孫可在網上寫低先人生平及對佢嘅感言，又可上載先人最鍾意食物、歌星偶像圖片，利用網絡科技告慰在天之靈。<br />\n<br />\n網頁有 facebook常用功能，可以邀請親友加入悼念之餘，又可以設定先人生忌同死忌等重要日子，到時會發訊息提醒親友，好貼心。呢個網頁只服務使用過食環署火化、骨灰龕位服務嘅先人，在世高官唔使驚俾人預先在網上悼念。食環署署長卓永興稱相信冇人咁無聊惡搞高官。市民可到「無盡思念」網站登記，網址係 [url]<a href=\"http://www.memorial.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.memorial.gov.hk&d=ugRGr0K6dq0P6yXV8xHYtGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=68e903b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.memorial.gov.hk</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"b4eb463957c54d53fbd4186187255ca2dfe35cee","tid":258593,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"網上打卡"},{"pid":"4cb5896671e33e577576fd4a986c912d5f47407b","tid":258593,"uid":7190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"將成個六四集會電子化算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa54ba8cd49b9097e4bb7065d4d65065d563c8e","tid":258593,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"咁我用google map當去左算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aa6ce3d217b9d644407851dc476eac253fea13","tid":258593,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://v026o.popscreen.com/eGlybzN0MTI=_o_the-blue-screen-army.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv026o.popscreen.com%2FeGlybzN0MTI%3D_o_the-blue-screen-army.jpg&h=41387c7d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}